[4.432925, "o", "\u001b[2mUse \u001b[32m'/'\u001b[39m for commands, \u001b[32m'!'\u001b[39m for shell. \u001b[32m'#'\u001b[39m to query, \u001b[32m'@'\u001b[39m to switch agents\r\nCTRL+T multiline, CTRL+Y copy last message, CTRL+E external editor.\r\nCTRL+Space or Tab for path completion. Use \u001b[35m/\u001b[95mattach\u001b[39m, `^file:`, or `^url:` for attachments. F10 to\u001b[5;1Hclear.\r\n\u001b(B\u001b[m"]
